HEADWORD: duplexer
<hw>du"plex*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Radio)</fld>
<def>a device which switches electronic circuitry so that a radio
antenna can function as either a transmitting or receiving
antenna.</def>⟦br⟧
